{"tid":867298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 懲教署：在囚人士不會在周日及節日工作！","createTime":"2018-10-18T14:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T12:24:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc73883e93aa9c374db3fb9577093159b524261","tid":867298,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T14:20:21.000Z","msg":"懲教署表示，根據法例規定，除確實必須的工作外，<span style=\"color: red;\">在囚人士不會在星期日及重要節日工作。</span>不過廚房必須全年運作，以維持在囚人士膳食供應，在廚房內工作的在囚人士每周休息安排為輪休制，分批在周內休息。<br />\n<br />\n在通訊方面，署方表示，在囚人士可按法例的規定收發信件，當中包括立法會議員、廉政專員及其他執法機構，而所有信件均會妥善記錄；在囚人士亦可透過家屬探訪、律師探訪或到訪的巡獄太平紳士，要求與議員或其他執法機構會面。發言人指過往有不少例子，有關方面在接獲通知後與在囚人士會面，跟進個案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1987729/org/e626dd574c0f51f20dbf1f504aa53811.jpg/u6_h7PoauW1wr3iqMmpbHItiujEsqIF8fY8JKn2PCSo?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1987729%2Forg%2Fe626dd574c0f51f20dbf1f504aa53811.jpg%2Fu6_h7PoauW1wr3iqMmpbHItiujEsqIF8fY8JKn2PCSo%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=b6c875d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/248602/%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E7%BD%B2-%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%96-%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E8%BC%AA%E4%BC%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F248602%2F%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%259B%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E5%25BB%259A%25E6%2588%25BF%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25A4%2596-%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E4%25BC%2591&d=r3KAKVFNaHluzyQg9s7QtkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=273dacdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/248602/%E